  "message": "test(macros): add compile-fail tests for proc-macro error messages (bd-12rb)\n\nAdd trybuild compile-fail tests verifying error messages for:\n- scope! without cx argument\n- scope! with return in body\n- scope! missing body block\n- spawn! with no arguments\n- #[conformance] missing spec attribute\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
